window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>When a traveling Egyptian exhibit stops in picturesque Pomme Valley, all hell breaks loose when a valuable artifact is stolen and a dead body turns up in an unexpected location.&nbsp;</p> <p>The prime suspect has already been identified, but there's a catch: He's more than 3,000 years old.&nbsp;</p> <p>Pomme Valley's newest crime-fighting crusaders are on the case with Sherlock, new packmate Watson, and their reluctant human, Zack.&nbsp;</p> <p>Can they solve the murder and locate the missing loot before any more misfortune can befall the town?</p>";